<opener><salute>Viro Doctissimo at<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> Celeberrimo
             <lb/>Petro Antonio <rs key="pers_DE-588-102552517" type="person">Michelotti</rs>
<lb/><abbr>S. P. D.</abbr>
<lb/><choice><abbr>Joh.</abbr><expan>Johannes</expan></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Bernoull<choice><orig><g ref="#j">j</g></orig><reg>i</reg></choice></rs>.</salute></opener>
<p><lb/>Respondissem citius ad ultimas Tuas <rs key="B_1720-05-17_991170515150805501" type="letter">litteras</rs><note type="editorial">Pietro Antonio Michelotti an Johann I Bernoulli, vom 17. Mai 1720</note>
<lb/>gratissimas, nisi in iisdem mihi spem
         <lb/>fecisses, Te mihi intra mensem iterum
         <lb/>scripturum ad faciendum me certiorem,
         <lb/>quid de itinere, quod meditaris in <rs key="place_VER-frankr" type="place">Galliam</rs>
<lb/>cum <choice><abbr>Illustr.</abbr><expan>Illustrissimo</expan></choice> et <choice><abbr>Excell.</abbr><expan>Excellentissimo</expan></choice> Equite Laurentio
         <lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-121843858" type="person">Theupolo</rs> apud Te deliberaveris et statueris;
         <lb/>Quia autem hactenus nil litterarum abs
         <lb/>Te accepi, nolu<choice><orig><g ref="#j">j</g></orig><reg>i</reg></choice> diutius differre responsionem;
         <lb/>Mihi sane gratissimum foret, si Te
         <lb/>in reditu Tuo ex <rs key="place_VER-frankr" type="place">Galliis</rs> per hanc urbem<!-- orttag -->
<lb/>iter facientem deosculari et amplexari possem;
         <lb/>Hoc tantum enixe rogo, ut recta ad me
         <lb/>divertas at<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> Hospitio et mensa mea (etsi tenui)
         <pb facs="1079169" n="2"/>
<lb/>fruaris per aliquod tempus; fortassis <rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person">Agnatus</rs> meus,
         <lb/>qui Te officiose salutat et qui nuper duxit <rs key="pers_DE-588-1089913346" type="person">uxorem</rs><note type="editorial">Nicolaus I Bernoulli hatte am 3. Juni 1720 Anna Maria Birr (1681-1747) geheiratet.</note>
<lb/>valde opulentam eundem honorem Tui pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>sentia
         <lb/>in <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>dibus suis gaudendi expetet; saltem alteruter nostr<choice><orig><g ref="#uhat">û</g></orig><reg>u</reg></choice>m
         <lb/>isthoc honoris pro certo sperabit. Quando apud Nos
         <lb/>fueris deliberabimus, num e re sit <rs key="pers_DE-588-118656503" type="person">filium</rs> meum
         <lb/>secundum Tecum in <rs key="place_KON-italie" type="place">Italiam</rs> mittere, interim
         <lb/>absolvet cursum suum Medicum at<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> suam
         <lb/>habebit <rs key="biblio_KGZSMV2E" type="biblio">Dissertationem</rs><note type="editorial">Bernoulli, Daniel St.1, Dissertatio Inauguralis Physico-Medica De Respiratione, Quam Consensu <choice><orig><g ref="#etlig">&amp;</g></orig><reg>et</reg></choice> Auctoritate Gratiosissimi Medicorum Ordinis in Universitate Patria Pro Summis in Arte Medica Honoribus <choice><orig><g ref="#etlig">&amp;</g></orig><reg>et</reg></choice> Privilegiis Doctoralibus rite consequendis, Ad diem 2. Septembr. MDCCXXI L.H.Q.S. Publico Examini subjicit Daniel Bernoulli, Joh. Fil. Basil., o.O. [Basileae]: Typis Johannis Ludovici Brandmülleri, o.J. [1721] - Werke 1, pp.61-83. Bibliographie zur Korrespondenz zwischen Johann I Bernoulli und Christian Wolff (provisorisch).</note> inauguralem, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> forte
         <lb/>tractabit de Respiratione; gratias vero debitas
         <lb/>ago pro cubili quod ipsi offers, nec non pro li<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>centi<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice>, quam ipsi concedis <choice><orig><g ref="#AE">Æ</g></orig><reg>Ae</reg></choice>gros Tuos Tecum
         <lb/>visitandi, ut in praxi Medica sese exercere
         <lb/>possit. Gaudeo quod annotationes me<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> in
         <lb/>Elegantem Tuam <rs key="biblio_M3G2JA79" type="biblio">Dissertationem</rs><note type="editorial">Michelotti, Pietro Antonio, De separatione fluidorum in corpore animali dissertatio physico-mechanico-medica, Venetiis (A. &amp; A. Pinelli) 1721. (Digitalisat bei BSB digital). Bibliographie zur Korrespondenz zwischen Johann I Bernoulli und Johann Jakob Scheuchzer.</note> Tibi haud displi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>cuerint. Scire aveo an perinde placuerint, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>
         <lb/>in <rs key="pers_DE-588-119507978" type="person">Jurinum</rs>, <rs key="pers_DE-588-1055365613" type="person">Keilium</rs>, et, ni fallor, adhuc in
         <lb/>alium quendam<!-- persontag --> co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>enti sumus; si co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>ode Tuo
         <lb/><rs key="biblio_M3G2JA79" type="biblio">operi</rs><note type="editorial">Meint vermutlich auch die Diss. Michelottis, evtl. mitt allem, was mitgedruckt wird: Michelotti, Pietro Antonio, De separatione fluidorum in corpore animali dissertatio physico-mechanico-medica, Venetiis (A. &amp; A. Pinelli) 1721. (Digitalisat bei BSB digital). Bibliographie zur Korrespondenz zwischen Johann I Bernoulli und Johann Jakob Scheuchzer.</note> inseri possunt, pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>sertim qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> ad velocitatem
         <lb/>aqu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> ex vase effluentis spectant mihi pergratum
         <pb facs="1079170" n="3"/>
         erit; Ne <rs key="pers_DE-588-119507978" type="person">Jurinus</rs> et alii<note type="editorial">Identifizierbar als einzelne Personen?</note> qui cum eo faciunt
         <lb/>Angli de Nobis tanquam victis triumphum
         <lb/>canant. Spero pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>laudatum Tuum <rs key="biblio_M3G2JA79" type="biblio">opus</rs><note type="editorial">Meint vermutlich auch die Diss Michelottis, evtl. mitt allem, was mitgedruckt wird: Michelotti, Pietro Antonio, De separatione fluidorum in corpore animali dissertatio physico-mechanico-medica, Venetiis (A. &amp; A. Pinelli) 1721. (Digitalisat bei BSB digital). Bibliographie zur Korrespondenz zwischen Johann I Bernoulli und Johann Jakob Scheuchzer.</note> posse
         <lb/>pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>lum evadere, antequam iter Tuum <rs key="place_VER-frankr" type="place">Gallic<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice></rs>
<lb/>aggrediaris, ita ut aliquod ejus exemplar in reditu
         <lb/>Tuo, ubi hac transieris, mihi asportari<note type="editorial">Im Manuskript "apportari" in "asportari" korrigiert, dabei ist "asportari" mit "mitgebracht werden" zu übersetzen.</note>  possis.
         <lb/>Quod superest, rogo, ut <rs key="pers_DE-588-117589144" type="person">filium</rs> meum, cui adjectas
         <lb/><rs key="brieftag" type="letter">litteras</rs><note type="editorial">Brief von Joh. I an Nic. II B.: Identifizieren! Im Briefinventar ist nur ein Brief vom 10. Oktober 1720 von Joh. I B. an Nic. II B. überliefert.</note> tradi cures, Tibi semper commendatum
         <lb/>habeas.</p> <closer><salute>Vale Vir Celeberrime et mihi favere
            <lb/>perge.</salute><dateline>Dabam <rs key="place_GEO-2661604" type="place">Basile<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> <choice><abbr>a. d.</abbr><expan>ad diem</expan></choice> <date when="1720-07-06">VI<choice><orig><g ref="#ndot">.</g></orig><reg></reg></choice> Julii 1720.</date></dateline></closer>
